dct_title_s: Geomorphic map of California and Nevada with portions of Oregon and Idaho
dct_description_sm: Shows railways, towns, counties and drainage.
From: Report on the California earthquake of April 18, 1906 "Map no. 1."
Unlike other issue, this does not show faults.
